What dmfIAM actually is
dmfIAM is an enterprise Identity Provider and Identity & Access Management platform.
It:
Is the system of record for identities
Manages authentication, authorization, and lifecycle
Integrates with AD and Microsoft Entra (not the other way around)
Correct mental model
dmfIAM = Identity Provider + Governance
Entra / AD = Directories & federation targets
Simple positioning sentence (use everywhere)
dmfIAM is an enterprise Identity Provider that centralizes authentication, authorization, and identity lifecycle — built for Swiss regulated environments.
